The dataset is publicly accessible for research and educational
purposes under an open access license that is provided by the
dataset's maintainers. The dataset is accessible through data
repositories that are present on websites such as Kaggle. The users
are required to adhere to the terms of use of the dataset, which
allows for non-commercial research usage and proper citation of
the original creators of the dataset.

Link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/emmarex/plantdisease